{"h791a6d09g3738g45bega4beg62529d087b04": ["You're wasting your time. This door is staying shut.", "1f76e748-d0d5-4cb5-8d0f-7fd96f14285b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "ee0c85d3-3035-3de7-22f7-7b199da36221"], "hbbd7a0e3gcb35g4edcg8d43g9d0fd37cb35e": ["You people have endangered the grove for long enough. Go away!", "1f76e748-d0d5-4cb5-8d0f-7fd96f14285b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "d440b6de-fbe8-d67d-07dd-ce988ffc1ff2"], "h1530c0b8g9089g4becg994ag3d1445a1148a": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "ce9c3c0d-171e-9b38-e2de-e94cbf1598c0"], "ha1bcd418ge3cdg4fa5g84acga7561fabff69": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "d69ca0ee-61bb-4f12-0beb-13916b00e031"], "h4cb75cc9g54e3g4726g9a19gfb5a2ed8eb5d": ["Go away! There's nothing in here for you - for <i>any </i>of you.", "1f76e748-d0d5-4cb5-8d0f-7fd96f14285b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "da7e18ff-df26-b077-0b92-6cb112ce87bd"], "he6f779c0g8648g43a4g91d8g75764d4cd60d": ["What's going on here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "a67abc8a-33a8-e809-b008-6838e496cc29"], "h7d6c196agae26g4b85ga995g94fc2f99c0ba": ["I said <i>go away</i>. You people have endangered this sacred place long enough.", "1f76e748-d0d5-4cb5-8d0f-7fd96f14285b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "92032ba0-f264-857c-05a0-8a36f7e4fdc6"], "h18572f33g836cg42b0gb280g68b8503562b6": ["This door is staying closed until you're gone, one way or another.", "1f76e748-d0d5-4cb5-8d0f-7fd96f14285b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "d7438911-690f-8cdd-e400-ab9416091645"], "hf9b18614ga670g4a8aga30cg237d07a83102": ["Come on now, open up! There's people out here who need shelter.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "6c28e459-c252-7b6e-f926-137d2eac6518"], "h12df557dg16abg4f56gbe69g2b549ab263b7": ["We've been more than generous already! We have to take care of the grove's future.", "1f76e748-d0d5-4cb5-8d0f-7fd96f14285b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "8fd99667-67af-cdd7-b78f-7cd83510d137"], "h84829e86g72d6g42a8gbab3g273d9b7e0a42": ["<i>Move away. </i>", "1f76e748-d0d5-4cb5-8d0f-7fd96f14285b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "996dc0a6-ac38-36e2-8a0a-011defc835bd"], "h2c114044g6139g4f96g9359g4175c845f525": ["Coward. Innocents are going to die, thanks to you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "b570ac0d-8ce9-bfbd-97ae-24c01d0c20f3"], "h2ac13b65g4dcfg46e0g8830gc3fd78a70eb8": ["Then this sacred grove can be a comfort to them in their final moments.", "1f76e748-d0d5-4cb5-8d0f-7fd96f14285b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "d579a3de-613c-7485-cf5e-becf0f789b01"], "hcd179fa8g471fg4847g9bfcg9445d971ec4e": ["But this door is staying closed. Now leave!", "1f76e748-d0d5-4cb5-8d0f-7fd96f14285b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "e5d7fc32-0aab-2634-8a17-be2a50f8e05a"], "he7db135dg7f57g49d2g860cg8186e9cace28": ["Go rejoin the others, kid.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "00e399dd-273b-c575-ceb9-f265d2dc1f22"], "h5bdfd4bcg7136g463fgb80ag0efe16b6e85d": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "33bdcc76-ba0b-f891-c011-2cc5c62196cc"], "h6685464eg5469g46cdg97b6g4d48f3e2dffe": ["You're a disgrace to this sacred grove. You should wither with shame.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "af106641-0f4e-cf9a-4db4-f263ad03e593"], "h21c42cf9gec95g4aa1gbd85g633d86c085b0": ["There's no shame in ensuring the sanctity of this grove. Now leave!", "1f76e748-d0d5-4cb5-8d0f-7fd96f14285b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "8885740a-fc64-3a83-01ff-0c8bb485eb11"], "h143c0caega225g473dgaf50ge859dcdb6190": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "255a6bfe-330c-a41c-b6e3-461e3ce75841"], "h600f81cag1e8ag4346gb876g2069f397b355": ["This door is staying shut - just be sensible and leave!", "1f76e748-d0d5-4cb5-8d0f-7fd96f14285b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "3defa4b0-c5dd-b036-ba50-0851ccdea554"], "ha0263ce5gb7a7g4b32g9093ge2437f93c978": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_LairDoor.html", "fe17dfbe-f71b-3445-d2fd-f63a624c61d2"]}